Johann Sebastian Bach (Marichi 21, 1685 - Julayi 28, 1750) anali wolemba wamkulu waku Germany munthawi ya Baroque. Bach amadziwika kuti ndi m'modzi mwa akatswiri ofunikira kwambiri komanso olemba mbiri yakale ku Europe. Anakhudzidwa kwambiri ndi olemba pambuyo pake monga Mozart, Beethoven ndi Brahms, ndipo adakwaniritsa mitundu yambiri ya nyimbo. Mbiri ya Bach ndiyokwera kwambiri pakati pa oimba nyimbo komanso olemba mbiri yakale.
